query:
/*+ NoNestLoop(l p s o) NoNestLoop(d l o p s c) */ select d.d_year,
s.s_nation,
p.p_category,
sum(l.l_revenue - l.l_supplycost) AS profit
from supplier AS s
inner join lineitem AS l
on l.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey AND s.s_region = 'AMERICA'
inner join part AS p
on l.l_partkey = p.p_partkey AND ( p.p_mfgr = 'MFGR#1' OR p.p_mfgr = 'MFGR#2')
inner join orders AS o
on l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey
inner join date AS d
on o.o_orderdate = d.d_datekey AND ( d.d_year = 1997 OR d.d_year = 1998)
inner join customer AS c
on o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey AND c.c_region = 'AMERICA' group by d.d_year, s.s_nation, p.p_category order by d.d_year, s.s_nation, p.p_category;
